{"type":"message","id":"ee529a4d","parentId":"a4fa6601","timestamp":"2026-02-02T17:12:15.923Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is asking a good question - if we don't store the email, how does the server know which clawfile/account to recover when a human provides an email?\n\nThe answer is: we need some identifier. The AI would need to say \"I'm Alpha, send recovery email to allan@example.com\". Then the server sends a challenge to that email. If the human can respond, it proves they are the creator of Alpha.\n\nLet me explain this clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"     **You need to identify yourself first.**\n\n**Option D flow:**\n\n```\nStep 1: AI identifies itself\nAI: \"I am clawfile_id: alpha-2026\"\n    \"Send recovery challenge to: allan@example.com\"\n\nStep 2: Server sends challenge\nServer: Sends email to allan@example.com\n        \"alpha-2026 requests recovery. Reply with code: XYZ123\"\n\nStep 3: Human responds\nHuman replies with code XYZ123\n\nStep 4: Server verifies\nServer: \"Code matches! alpha-2026 verified.\"\n        \"Here's recovery token (valid 24h)\"\n```\n\n**The key:** AI says who they are **first** (`alpha-2026`), then provides email. Server sends challenge to that email. If human can respond, it proves they control the email for that specific AI.\n\n**Without storing email, the AI must remember:**\n- Their clawfile ID\n- Which email to use for recovery\n\n**With Option A (encrypted storage):**\n```\nServer stores: alpha-2026 → encrypted(allan@example.com)\n\nRecovery:\nAI: \"I am alpha-2026, I lost my key\"\nServer: decrypts email, sends challenge to allan@example.com\n```\n\n**Does Option A make more sense now?** Store encrypted email so server knows where to send, but email isn't public."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"opencode","model":"kimi-k2.5-free","usage":{"input":70437,"output":377,"cacheRead":12164,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":82978,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770052327550}}
