pp\n- ❌ **Sync issues** — Clock drift can cause failures\n\n**Use case:** Secondary verification for recovery. Email + TOTP = strong 2FA.\n\n**Adding as option #8?** Good for high-security AI."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"opencode","model":"kimi-k2.5-free","usage":{"input":73727,"output":465,"cacheRead":12098,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":86290,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770052924029}}
