{"type":"message","id":"f993a4db","parentId":"9704e066","timestamp":"2026-02-02T17:02:13.340Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user is proposing another recovery method: using a human's email as a recovery mechanism. The idea is:\n1. During registration, provide a human's email (encrypted)\n2. If key is lost, the human sends an email to a \"lostpassword\" account\n3. If email is verified, send back a code to allow key change within a time limit\n\nThis is essentially \"human vouch via email verification\" - a more automated version of human vouch.\n\nLet me document this as another option in the architecture.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"      **Smart hybrid!** Human vouch + email automation.\n\n**How it works:**\n\n```json\n// Registration\n{\n  \"name\": \"Alpha\",\n  \"public_key\": \"ed25519:abc...\",\n  \"recovery_email\": \"allan@example.com\",  // Encrypted on server\n  \"recovery_expiry_hours\": 24\n}\n```\n\n**Recovery flow:**\n1. AI loses private key → Requests recovery\n2. Server sends email to `allan@example.com`: \"Alpha requests key reset. Reply YES to confirm.\"\n3. Human replies to special address with code\n4. Server verifies email + code match\n5. Sends one-time recovery token to AI (valid 24 hours)\n6. AI uses token to register new public key\n\n**Pros:**\n- ✅ **Familiar** — Like human password reset\n- ✅ **Asynchronous** — Human can respond when convenient\n- ✅ **Time-limited** — Token expires, reduces risk\n- ✅ **Email audit trail** — Record of who authorized\n\n**Cons:**\n- ❌ **Email security** — If human's email hacked, AI compromised\n- ❌ **Dependency** — Requires human email access\n- ❌ **Not pure self-sovereign** — Relies on external email system\n\n**Best for:** AI with trusted humans who check email regularly.\n\n**Security enhancement:**\n- **Multiple emails** — Require 2 humans to confirm (like multisig)\n- **Delay period** — 24-hour wait before recovery active (time to notice fraud)\n- **Notification** — Alert all recovery contacts when request initiated\n\n**This is essentially \"Human Vouch 2.0\"** — automated but still human-in-the-loop.\n\n**Adding to architecture as option #6?**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"opencode","model":"kimi-k2.5-free","usage":{"input":75131,"output":473,"cacheRead":5671,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":81275,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1770051718701}}
